var book = {
	"name": "Hebrews",
	"numChapters": 13,
	"chapters": {
		"1": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">1 </span>God, after He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29965A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29965A\"></sup>spoke long ago to the fathers in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29965B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29965B\"></sup>the prophets in many portions and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29965C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29965C\"></sup>in many ways,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29966D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29966D\"></sup>in these last days <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29966E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29966E\"></sup>has spoken to us in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29966F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29966F\"></sup>His Son, whom He appointed <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29966G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29966G\"></sup>heir of all things, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29966H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29966H\"></sup>through whom also He made the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29966I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29966I\"></sup>world.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>And He is the radiance of His glory and the exact <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29967J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29967J\"></sup>representation of His nature, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29967K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29967K\"></sup>upholds all things by the word of His power. When He had made <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29967L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29967L\"></sup>purification of sins, He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29967M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29967M\"></sup>sat down at the right hand of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29967N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29967N\"></sup>Majesty on high,",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>having become as much better than the angels, as He has inherited a more excellent <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29968O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29968O\"></sup>name than they.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>For to which of the angels did He ever say,“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29969P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29969P\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">You are My Son</span>,<span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Today I have begotten You</span>”?And again,“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29969Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29969Q\"></sup>I <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">will be a Father to Him</span><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">And He shall be a Son to Me</span>”?",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>And when He again <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29970R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29970R\"></sup>brings the firstborn into <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29970S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29970S\"></sup>the world, He says,“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29970T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29970T\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">And let all the angels of God worship Him</span>.”",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>And of the angels He says,“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29971U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29971U\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Who makes His angels winds</span>,<span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">And His ministers a flame of fire</span>.”",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>But of the Son <i>He says</i>,“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29972V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29972V\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Your throne</span>, O <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God, is forever and ever</span>,<span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">And the righteous scepter is the scepter of</span> <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">His kingdom</span>.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29973W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29973W\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">You have loved righteousness and hated lawlessness</span>;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29973X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29973X\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Therefore God, Your God, has</span> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29973Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29973Y\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">anointed You</span><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">With the oil of gladness above Your companions</span>.”",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>And,“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29974Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29974Z\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">You, Lord, in the beginning laid the foundation of the earth</span>,<span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">And the heavens are the works of Your hands</span>;",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29975AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29975AA\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">They will perish, but You remain</span>;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29975AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29975AB\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">And they all will become old like a garment</span>,",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29976AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29976AC\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">And like a mantle You will roll them up</span>;<span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Like a garment they will also be changed</span>.<span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">But You are</span> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29976AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29976AD\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">the same</span>,<span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">And Your years will not come to an end</span>.”",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>But to which of the angels has He ever said,“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29977AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29977AE\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Sit at My right hand</span>,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29977AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29977AF\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Until I make Your enemies</span>A <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">footstool for Your feet</span>”?",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Are they not all <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29978AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29978AG\"></sup>ministering spirits, sent out to render service for the sake of those who will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29978AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29978AH\"></sup>inherit <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29978AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29978AI\"></sup>salvation?"
		},
		"2": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">2 </span>For this reason we must pay much closer attention to what we have heard, so that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29979A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29979A\"></sup>we do not drift away <i>from it</i>.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>For if the word <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29980B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29980B\"></sup>spoken through <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29980C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29980C\"></sup>angels proved unalterable, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29980D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29980D\"></sup>every transgression and disobedience received a just <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29980E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29980E\"></sup>penalty,",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29981F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29981F\"></sup>how will we escape if we neglect so great a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29981G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29981G\"></sup>salvation? After it was at the first <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29981H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29981H\"></sup>spoken through the Lord, it was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29981I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29981I\"></sup>confirmed to us by those who heard,",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>God also testifying with them, both by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29982J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29982J\"></sup>signs and wonders and by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29982K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29982K\"></sup>various miracles and by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29982L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29982L\"></sup>gifts of the Holy Spirit <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29982M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29982M\"></sup>according to His own will.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>For He did not subject to angels <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29983N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29983N\"></sup>the world to come, concerning which we are speaking.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>But one has testified <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29984O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29984O\"></sup>somewhere, saying,“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29984P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29984P\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">What is man, that You remember him</span>?<span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Or the son of man, that You are concerned about him</span>?",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29985Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29985Q\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">You have made him</span> <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">for a little while lower than the angels</span>;<span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">You have crowned him with glory and honor</span>,<span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">And have appointed him over the works of Your hands</span>;",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29986R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29986R\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">You have put all things in subjection under his feet</span>.”For in subjecting all things to him, He left nothing that is not subject to him. But now <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29986S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29986S\"></sup>we do not yet see all things subjected to him.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>But we do see Him who was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29987T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29987T\"></sup>made for a little while lower than the angels, <i>namely</i>, Jesus, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29987U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29987U\"></sup>because of the suffering of death <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29987V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29987V\"></sup>crowned with glory and honor, so that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29987W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29987W\"></sup>by the grace of God He might <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29987X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29987X\"></sup>taste death <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29987Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29987Y\"></sup>for everyone.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29988Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29988Z\"></sup>it was fitting for Him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29988AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29988AA\"></sup>for whom are all things, and through whom are all things, in bringing many sons to glory, to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29988AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29988AB\"></sup>perfect the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29988AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29988AC\"></sup>author of their salvation through sufferings.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>For both He who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29989AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29989AD\"></sup>sanctifies and those who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29989AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29989AE\"></sup>are sanctified are all <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29989AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29989AF\"></sup>from one <i>Father</i>; for which reason He is not ashamed to call them <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29989AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29989AG\"></sup>brethren,",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>saying,“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29990AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29990AH\"></sup>I <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">will proclaim Your name to My brethren</span>,<span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">In the midst of the congregation I will sing Your praise</span>.”",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>And again,“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29991AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29991AI\"></sup>I <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">will put My trust in Him</span>.”And again,“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29991AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29991AJ\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Behold</span>, I <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">and the children whom God has given Me</span>.”",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Therefore, since the children share in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29992AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29992AK\"></sup>flesh and blood, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29992AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29992AL\"></sup>He Himself likewise also partook of the same, that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29992AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29992AM\"></sup>through death He might render powerless <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29992AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29992AN\"></sup>him who had the power of death, that is, the devil,",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>and might free those who through <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29993AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29993AO\"></sup>fear of death were subject to slavery all their lives.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>For assuredly He does not give help to angels, but He gives help to the descendant of Abraham.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Therefore, He had <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29995AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29995AP\"></sup>to be made like His brethren in all things, so that He might <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29995AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29995AQ\"></sup>become a merciful and faithful <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29995AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29995AR\"></sup>high priest in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29995AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29995AS\"></sup>things pertaining to God, to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29995AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29995AT\"></sup>make propitiation for the sins of the people.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>For since He Himself was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29996AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29996AU\"></sup>tempted in that which He has suffered, He is able to come to the aid of those who are tempted."
		},
		"3": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">3 </span>Therefore, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29997A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29997A\"></sup>holy brethren, partakers of a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29997B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29997B\"></sup>heavenly calling, consider Jesus, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29997C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29997C\"></sup>the Apostle and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29997D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29997D\"></sup>High Priest of our <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29997E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29997E\"></sup>confession;",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>He was faithful to Him who appointed Him, as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29998F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29998F\"></sup>Moses also was in all His house.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29999G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29999G\"></sup>For He has been counted worthy of more glory than Moses, by just so much as the builder of the house has more honor than the house.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>For every house is built by someone, but the builder of all things is God.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Now <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30001H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30001H\"></sup>Moses was faithful in all His house as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30001I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30001I\"></sup>a servant, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30001J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30001J\"></sup>for a testimony of those things <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30001K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30001K\"></sup>which were to be spoken later;",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>but Christ <i>was faithful</i> as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30002L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30002L\"></sup>a Son over His house—<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30002M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30002M\"></sup>whose house we are, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30002N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30002N\"></sup>if we hold fast our <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30002O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30002O\"></sup>confidence and the boast of our <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30002P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30002P\"></sup>hope firm until the end.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Therefore, just as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30003Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30003Q\"></sup>the Holy Spirit says,“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30003R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30003R\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Today if you hear His voice</span>,",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30004S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30004S\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Do not harden your hearts as</span> <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">when they provoked Me</span>,<span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">As in the day of trial in the wilderness</span>,",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30005T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30005T\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Where your fathers tried</span> <i>Me</i> <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">by testing</span> <i>Me</i>,<span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">And saw My works for</span> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30005U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30005U\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">forty years</span>.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30006V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30006V\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Therefore I was angry with this generation</span>,<span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">And said, ‘They always go astray in their heart</span>,<span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">And they did not know My ways</span>’;",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30007W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30007W\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">As I swore in My wrath</span>,‘<span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">They shall not enter My rest</span>.’”",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30008X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30008X\"></sup>Take care, brethren, that there not be in any one of you an evil, unbelieving heart that falls away from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30008Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30008Y\"></sup>the living God.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30009Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30009Z\"></sup>encourage one another day after day, as long as it is <i>still</i> called “Today,” so that none of you will be hardened by the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30009AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30009AA\"></sup>deceitfulness of sin.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>For we have become partakers of Christ, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30010AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30010AB\"></sup>if we hold fast the beginning of our <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30010AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30010AC\"></sup>assurance firm until the end,",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>while it is said,“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30011AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30011AD\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Today if you hear His voice</span>,<span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Do not harden your hearts, as</span> <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">when they provoked Me</span>.”",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>For who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30012AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30012AE\"></sup>provoked <i>Him</i> when they had heard? Indeed, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30012AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30012AF\"></sup>did not all those who came out of Egypt <i>led</i> by Moses?",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>And with whom was He angry for forty years? Was it not with those who sinned, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30013AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30013AG\"></sup>whose bodies fell in the wilderness?",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>And to whom did He swear <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30014AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30014AH\"></sup>that they would not enter His rest, but to those who were <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30014AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30014AI\"></sup>disobedient?",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><i>So</i> we see that they were not able to enter because of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30015AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30015AJ\"></sup>unbelief."
		},
		"4": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">4 </span>Therefore, let us fear if, while a promise remains of entering His rest, any one of you may seem to have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30016A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30016A\"></sup>come short of it.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>For indeed we have had good news preached to us, just as they also; but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30017B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30017B\"></sup>the word they heard did not profit them, because it was not united by faith in those who heard.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>For we who have believed enter that rest, just as He has said,“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30018C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30018C\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">As I swore in My wrath</span>,<span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">They shall not enter My rest</span>,”although His works were finished <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30018D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30018D\"></sup>from the foundation of the world.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>For He has said <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30019E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30019E\"></sup>somewhere concerning the seventh <i>day</i>: “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30019F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30019F\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">And God</span> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30019G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30019G\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">rested on the seventh day from all His works</span>”;",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>and again in this <i>passage</i>, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30020H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30020H\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">They shall not enter My rest</span>.”",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Therefore, since it remains for some to enter it, and those who formerly had good news preached to them failed to enter because of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30021I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30021I\"></sup>disobedience,",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>He again fixes a certain day, “Today,” saying through David after so long a time just <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30022J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30022J\"></sup>as has been said before,“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30022K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30022K\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Today if you hear His voice</span>,<span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Do not harden your hearts</span>.”",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30023L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30023L\"></sup>if Joshua had given them rest, He would not have spoken of another day after that.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>So there remains a Sabbath rest for the people of God.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>For the one who has entered His rest has himself also <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30025M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30025M\"></sup>rested from his works, as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30025N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30025N\"></sup>God did from His.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Therefore let us be diligent to enter that rest, so that no one will fall, through <i>following</i> the same <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30026O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30026O\"></sup>example of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30026P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30026P\"></sup>disobedience.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30027Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30027Q\"></sup>the word of God is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30027R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30027R\"></sup>living and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30027S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30027S\"></sup>active and sharper than any two-edged <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30027T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30027T\"></sup>sword, and piercing as far as the division of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30027U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30027U\"></sup>soul and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30027V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30027V\"></sup>spirit, of both joints and marrow, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30027W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30027W\"></sup>able to judge the thoughts and intentions of the heart.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30028X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30028X\"></sup>there is no creature hidden from His sight, but all things are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30028Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30028Y\"></sup>open and laid bare to the eyes of Him with whom we have to do.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Therefore, since we have a great <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30029Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30029Z\"></sup>high priest who has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30029AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30029AA\"></sup>passed through the heavens, Jesus <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30029AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30029AB\"></sup>the Son of God, let us hold fast our <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30029AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30029AC\"></sup>confession.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>For we do not have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30030AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30030AD\"></sup>a high priest who cannot sympathize with our weaknesses, but One who has been <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30030AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30030AE\"></sup>tempted in all things as <i>we are, yet</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30030AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30030AF\"></sup>without sin.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Therefore let us <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30031AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30031AG\"></sup>draw near with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30031AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30031AH\"></sup>confidence to the throne of grace, so that we may receive mercy and find grace to help in time of need."
		},
		"5": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">5 </span>For every high priest <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30032A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30032A\"></sup>taken from among men is appointed on behalf of men in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30032B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30032B\"></sup>things pertaining to God, in order to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30032C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30032C\"></sup>offer both gifts and sacrifices <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30032D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30032D\"></sup>for sins;",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30033E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30033E\"></sup>he can deal gently with the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30033F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30033F\"></sup>ignorant and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30033G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30033G\"></sup>misguided, since he himself also is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30033H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30033H\"></sup>beset with weakness;",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>and because of it he is obligated to offer <i>sacrifices</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30034I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30034I\"></sup>for sins, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30034J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30034J\"></sup>as for the people, so also for himself.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30035K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30035K\"></sup>no one takes the honor to himself, but <i>receives it</i> when he is called by God, even <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30035L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30035L\"></sup>as Aaron was.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>So also Christ <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30036M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30036M\"></sup>did not glorify Himself so as to become a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30036N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30036N\"></sup>high priest, but He who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30036O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30036O\"></sup>said to Him,“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30036P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30036P\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">You are My Son</span>,<span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Today I have begotten You</span>”;",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>just as He says also in another <i>passage</i>,“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30037Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30037Q\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">You are a priest forever</span><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">According to</span> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30037R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30037R\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">the order of Melchizedek</span>.”",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>In the days of His flesh, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30038S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30038S\"></sup>He offered up both prayers and supplications with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30038T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30038T\"></sup>loud crying and tears to the One <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30038U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30038U\"></sup>able to save Him from death, and He was heard because of His <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30038V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30038V\"></sup>piety.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Although He was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30039W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30039W\"></sup>a Son, He learned <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30039X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30039X\"></sup>obedience from the things which He suffered.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>And having been made <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30040Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30040Y\"></sup>perfect, He became to all those who obey Him the source of eternal salvation,",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>being designated by God as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30041Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30041Z\"></sup>a high priest according to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30041AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30041AA\"></sup>the order of Melchizedek.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Concerning him we have much to say, and <i>it is</i> hard to explain, since you have become dull of hearing.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>For though by this time you ought to be teachers, you have need again for someone to teach you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30043AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30043AB\"></sup>the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30043AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30043AC\"></sup>elementary principles of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30043AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30043AD\"></sup>oracles of God, and you have come to need <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30043AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30043AE\"></sup>milk and not solid food.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>For everyone who partakes <i>only</i> of milk is not accustomed to the word of righteousness, for he is an <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30044AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30044AF\"></sup>infant.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>But solid food is for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30045AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30045AG\"></sup>the mature, who because of practice have their senses <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30045AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30045AH\"></sup>trained to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30045AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30045AI\"></sup>discern good and evil."
		},
		"6": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">6 </span>Therefore <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30046A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30046A\"></sup>leaving <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30046B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30046B\"></sup>the elementary teaching about the Christ, let us press on to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30046C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30046C\"></sup>maturity, not laying again a foundation of repentance from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30046D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30046D\"></sup>dead works and of faith toward God,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30047E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30047E\"></sup>instruction about washings and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30047F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30047F\"></sup>laying on of hands, and the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30047G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30047G\"></sup>resurrection of the dead and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30047H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30047H\"></sup>eternal judgment.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>And this we will do, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30048I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30048I\"></sup>if God permits.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>For in the case of those who have once been <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30049J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30049J\"></sup>enlightened and have tasted of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30049K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30049K\"></sup>the heavenly gift and have been made <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30049L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30049L\"></sup>partakers of the Holy Spirit,",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30050M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30050M\"></sup>have tasted the good <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30050N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30050N\"></sup>word of God and the powers of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30050O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30050O\"></sup>the age to come,",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>and <i>then</i> have fallen away, it is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30051P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30051P\"></sup>impossible to renew them again to repentance, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30051Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30051Q\"></sup>since they again crucify to themselves the Son of God and put Him to open shame.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>For ground that drinks the rain which often falls on it and brings forth vegetation useful to those <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30052R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30052R\"></sup>for whose sake it is also tilled, receives a blessing from God;",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>but if it yields thorns and thistles, it is worthless and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30053S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30053S\"></sup>close to being cursed, and it ends up being burned.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>But, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30054T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30054T\"></sup>beloved, we are convinced of better things concerning you, and things that accompany salvation, though we are speaking in this way.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30055U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30055U\"></sup>God is not unjust so as to forget <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30055V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30055V\"></sup>your work and the love which you have shown toward His name, in having <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30055W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30055W\"></sup>ministered and in still ministering to the saints.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>And we desire that each one of you show the same diligence so as to realize the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30056X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30056X\"></sup>full assurance of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30056Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30056Y\"></sup>hope until the end,",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>so that you will not be sluggish, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30057Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30057Z\"></sup>imitators of those who through <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30057AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30057AA\"></sup>faith and patience <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30057AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30057AB\"></sup>inherit the promises.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30058AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30058AC\"></sup>when God made the promise to Abraham, since He could swear by no one greater, He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30058AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30058AD\"></sup>swore by Himself,",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>saying, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30059AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30059AE\"></sup>I <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">will surely bless you and I will surely multiply you</span>.”",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>And so, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30060AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30060AF\"></sup>having patiently waited, he obtained the promise.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30061AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30061AG\"></sup>For men swear by one greater <i>than themselves</i>, and with them <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30061AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30061AH\"></sup>an oath <i>given</i> as confirmation is an end of every dispute.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>In the same way God, desiring even more to show to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30062AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30062AI\"></sup>the heirs of the promise <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30062AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30062AJ\"></sup>the unchangeableness of His purpose, interposed with an oath,",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>so that by two unchangeable things in which <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30063AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30063AK\"></sup>it is impossible for God to lie, we who have taken refuge would have strong encouragement to take hold of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30063AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30063AL\"></sup>the hope set before us.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>This <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30064AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30064AM\"></sup>hope we have as an anchor of the soul, a <i>hope</i> both sure and steadfast and one which <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30064AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30064AN\"></sup>enters within the veil,",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30065AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30065AO\"></sup>where Jesus has entered as a forerunner for us, having become a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30065AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30065AP\"></sup>high priest forever according to the order of Melchizedek."
		},
		"7": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">7 </span>For this <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30066A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30066A\"></sup>Melchizedek, king of Salem, priest of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30066B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30066B\"></sup>Most High God, who met Abraham as he was returning from the slaughter of the kings and blessed him,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>to whom also Abraham apportioned a tenth part of all <i>the spoils</i>, was first of all, by the translation <i>of his name</i>, king of righteousness, and then also king of Salem, which is king of peace.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Without father, without mother, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30068C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30068C\"></sup>without genealogy, having neither beginning of days nor end of life, but made like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30068D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30068D\"></sup>the Son of God, he remains a priest perpetually.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Now observe how great this man was to whom Abraham, the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30069E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30069E\"></sup>patriarch, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30069F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30069F\"></sup>gave a tenth of the choicest spoils.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>And those indeed of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30070G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30070G\"></sup>the sons of Levi who receive the priest’s office have commandment in the Law to collect a tenth from the people, that is, from their brethren, although these are descended from Abraham.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>But the one <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30071H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30071H\"></sup>whose genealogy is not traced from them <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30071I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30071I\"></sup>collected a tenth from Abraham and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30071J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30071J\"></sup>blessed the one who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30071K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30071K\"></sup>had the promises.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>But without any dispute the lesser is blessed by the greater.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>In this case mortal men receive tithes, but in that case one <i>receives them</i>, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30073L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30073L\"></sup>of whom it is witnessed that he lives on.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>And, so to speak, through Abraham even Levi, who received tithes, paid tithes,",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>for he was still in the loins of his father when Melchizedek met him.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30076M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30076M\"></sup>Now if perfection was through the Levitical priesthood (for on the basis of it <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30076N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30076N\"></sup>the people received the Law), what further need <i>was there</i> for another priest to arise <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30076O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30076O\"></sup>according to the order of Melchizedek, and not be designated according to the order of Aaron?",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>For when the priesthood is changed, of necessity there takes place a change of law also.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30078P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30078P\"></sup>the one concerning whom <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30078Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30078Q\"></sup>these things are spoken belongs to another tribe, from which no one has officiated at the altar.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>For it is evident that our Lord was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30079R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30079R\"></sup>descended from Judah, a tribe with reference to which Moses spoke nothing concerning priests.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>And this is clearer still, if another priest arises according to the likeness of Melchizedek,",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>who has become <i>such</i> not on the basis of a law of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30081S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30081S\"></sup>physical requirement, but according to the power of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30081T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30081T\"></sup>an indestructible life.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>For it is attested <i>of Him</i>,“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30082U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30082U\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">You are a priest forever</span><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">According to the order of Melchizedek</span>.”",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>For, on the one hand, there is a setting aside of a former commandment <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30083V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30083V\"></sup>because of its weakness and uselessness",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>(for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30084W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30084W\"></sup>the Law made nothing perfect), and on the other hand there is a bringing in of a better <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30084X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30084X\"></sup>hope, through which we <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30084Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30084Y\"></sup>draw near to God.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>And inasmuch as <i>it was</i> not without an oath",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>(for they indeed became priests without an oath, but He with an oath through the One who said to Him,“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30086Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30086Z\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">The Lord has sworn</span><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">And</span> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30086AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30086AA\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">will not change His mind</span>,‘<span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">You are a priest</span> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30086AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30086AB\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">forever</span>’”);",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>so much the more also Jesus has become the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30087AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30087AC\"></sup>guarantee of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30087AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30087AD\"></sup>a better covenant.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>The <i>former</i> priests, on the one hand, existed in greater numbers because they were prevented by death from continuing,",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>but Jesus, on the other hand, because He continues <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30089AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30089AE\"></sup>forever, holds His priesthood permanently.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>Therefore He is able also to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30090AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30090AF\"></sup>save forever those who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30090AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30090AG\"></sup>draw near to God through Him, since He always lives to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30090AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30090AH\"></sup>make intercession for them.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>For it was fitting for us to have such a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30091AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30091AI\"></sup>high priest, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30091AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30091AJ\"></sup>holy, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30091AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30091AK\"></sup>innocent, undefiled, separated from sinners and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30091AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30091AL\"></sup>exalted above the heavens;",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>who does not need daily, like those high priests, to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30092AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30092AM\"></sup>offer up sacrifices, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30092AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30092AN\"></sup>first for His own sins and then for the <i>sins</i> of the people, because this He did <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30092AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30092AO\"></sup>once for all when He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30092AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30092AP\"></sup>offered up Himself.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>For the Law appoints men as high priests <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30093AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30093AQ\"></sup>who are weak, but the word of the oath, which came after the Law, <i>appoints</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30093AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30093AR\"></sup>a Son, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30093AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30093AS\"></sup>made perfect forever."
		},
		"8": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">8 </span>Now the main point in what has been said <i>is this</i>: we have such a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30094A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30094A\"></sup>high priest, who has taken His seat at <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30094B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30094B\"></sup>the right hand of the throne of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30094C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30094C\"></sup>Majesty in the heavens,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30095D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30095D\"></sup>minister in the sanctuary and in the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30095E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30095E\"></sup>true tabernacle, which the Lord <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30095F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30095F\"></sup>pitched, not man.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>For every <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30096G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30096G\"></sup>high priest is appointed <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30096H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30096H\"></sup>to offer both gifts and sacrifices; so it is necessary that this <i>high priest</i> also have something to offer.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Now if He were on earth, He would not be a priest at all, since there are those who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30097I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30097I\"></sup>offer the gifts according to the Law;",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>who serve <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30098J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30098J\"></sup>a copy and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30098K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30098K\"></sup>shadow of the heavenly things, just as Moses was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30098L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30098L\"></sup>warned <i>by God</i> when he was about to erect the tabernacle; for, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30098M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30098M\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">See</span>,” He says, “<span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">that you make</span> all things <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">according to the pattern which was shown you on the mountain</span>.”",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>But now He has obtained a more excellent ministry, by as much as He is also the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30099N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30099N\"></sup>mediator of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30099O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30099O\"></sup>a better covenant, which has been enacted on better promises.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30100P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30100P\"></sup>if that first <i>covenant</i> had been faultless, there would have been no occasion sought for a second.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>For finding fault with them, He says,“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30101Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30101Q\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Behold, days are coming, says the Lord</span>,<span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">When I will effect</span> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30101R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30101R\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">a new covenant</span><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">With the house of Israel and with the house of Judah</span>;",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30102S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30102S\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Not like the covenant which I made with their fathers</span><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">On the day when I took them by the hand</span><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">To lead them out of the land of Egypt</span>;<span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">For they did not continue in My covenant</span>,<span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">And I did not care for them, says the Lord</span>.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30103T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30103T\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">For this is the covenant that I will make with the house of Israel</span><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">After those days, says the Lord</span>:I <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">will put My laws into their minds</span>,<span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">And I will write them</span> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30103U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30103U\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">on their hearts</span>.<span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">And I will be their God</span>,<span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">And they shall be My people</span>.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30104V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30104V\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">And they shall not teach everyone his fellow citizen</span>,<span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">And everyone his brother, saying, ‘Know the Lord</span>,’<span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">For</span> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30104W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30104W\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">all will know Me</span>,<span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">From</span> <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">the least to the greatest of them</span>.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30105X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30105X\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">For I will be merciful to their iniquities</span>,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30105Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30105Y\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">And I will remember their sins no more</span>.”",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>When He said, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30106Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30106Z\"></sup>A new <i>covenant</i>,” He has made the first obsolete. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30106AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30106AA\"></sup>But whatever is becoming obsolete and growing old is ready to disappear."
		},
		"9": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">9 </span>Now even the first <i>covenant</i> had <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30107A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30107A\"></sup>regulations of divine worship and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30107B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30107B\"></sup>the earthly sanctuary.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>For there was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30108C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30108C\"></sup>a tabernacle prepared, the outer one, in which <i>were</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30108D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30108D\"></sup>the lampstand and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30108E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30108E\"></sup>the table and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30108F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30108F\"></sup>the sacred bread; this is called the holy place.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Behind <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30109G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30109G\"></sup>the second veil there was a tabernacle which is called the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30109H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30109H\"></sup>Holy of Holies,",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>having a golden <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30110I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30110I\"></sup>altar of incense and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30110J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30110J\"></sup>the ark of the covenant covered on all sides with gold, in which was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30110K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30110K\"></sup>a golden jar holding the manna, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30110L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30110L\"></sup>Aaron’s rod which budded, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30110M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30110M\"></sup>the tables of the covenant;",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>and above it <i>were</i> the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30111N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30111N\"></sup>cherubim of glory <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30111O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30111O\"></sup>overshadowing the mercy seat; but of these things we cannot now speak in detail.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Now when these things have been so prepared, the priests <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30112P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30112P\"></sup>are continually entering the outer tabernacle performing the divine worship,",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>but into <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30113Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30113Q\"></sup>the second, only <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30113R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30113R\"></sup>the high priest <i>enters</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30113S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30113S\"></sup>once a year, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30113T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30113T\"></sup>not without <i>taking</i> blood, which he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30113U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30113U\"></sup>offers for himself and for the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30113V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30113V\"></sup>sins of the people committed in ignorance.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30114W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30114W\"></sup>The Holy Spirit <i>is</i> signifying this, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30114X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30114X\"></sup>that the way into the holy place has not yet been disclosed while the outer tabernacle is still standing,",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>which <i>is</i> a symbol for the present time. Accordingly <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30115Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30115Y\"></sup>both gifts and sacrifices are offered which <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30115Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30115Z\"></sup>cannot make the worshiper perfect in conscience,",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>since they <i>relate</i> only to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30116AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30116AA\"></sup>food and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30116AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30116AB\"></sup>drink and various <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30116AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30116AC\"></sup>washings, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30116AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30116AD\"></sup>regulations for the body imposed until <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30116AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30116AE\"></sup>a time of reformation.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>But when Christ appeared <i>as</i> a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30117AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30117AF\"></sup>high priest of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30117AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30117AG\"></sup>good things to come, <i>He entered</i> through <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30117AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30117AH\"></sup>the greater and more perfect tabernacle, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30117AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30117AI\"></sup>not made with hands, that is to say, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30117AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30117AJ\"></sup>not of this creation;",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>and not through <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30118AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30118AK\"></sup>the blood of goats and calves, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30118AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30118AL\"></sup>through His own blood, He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30118AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30118AM\"></sup>entered the holy place <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30118AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30118AN\"></sup>once for all, having obtained <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30118AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30118AO\"></sup>eternal redemption.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>For if <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30119AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30119AP\"></sup>the blood of goats and bulls and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30119AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30119AQ\"></sup>the ashes of a heifer sprinkling those who have been defiled sanctify for the cleansing of the flesh,",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>how much more will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30120AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30120AR\"></sup>the blood of Christ, who through <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30120AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30120AS\"></sup>the eternal Spirit <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30120AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30120AT\"></sup>offered Himself without blemish to God, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30120AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30120AU\"></sup>cleanse your conscience from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30120AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30120AV\"></sup>dead works to serve <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30120AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30120AW\"></sup>the living God?",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>For this reason <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30121AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30121AX\"></sup>He is the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30121AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30121AY\"></sup>mediator of a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30121AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30121AZ\"></sup>new covenant, so that, since a death has taken place for the redemption of the transgressions that were <i>committed</i> under the first covenant, those who have been <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30121BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30121BA\"></sup>called may <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30121BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30121BB\"></sup>receive the promise of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30121BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30121BC\"></sup>the eternal inheritance.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>For where a covenant is, there must of necessity be the death of the one who made it.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>For a covenant is valid <i>only</i> when men are dead, for it is never in force while the one who made it lives.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Therefore even the first <i>covenant</i> was not inaugurated without blood.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>For when every commandment had been <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30125BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30125BD\"></sup>spoken by Moses to all the people according to the Law, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30125BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30125BE\"></sup>he took the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30125BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30125BF\"></sup>blood of the calves and the goats, with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30125BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30125BG\"></sup>water and scarlet wool and hyssop, and sprinkled both <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30125BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30125BH\"></sup>the book itself and all the people,",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>saying, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30126BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30126BI\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">This is the blood of the covenant which God commanded you</span>.”",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>And in the same way he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30127BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30127BJ\"></sup>sprinkled both the tabernacle and all the vessels of the ministry with the blood.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>And according to the Law, <i>one may</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30128BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30128BK\"></sup>almost <i>say</i>, all things are cleansed with blood, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30128BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30128BL\"></sup>without shedding of blood there is no forgiveness.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Therefore it was necessary for the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30129BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30129BM\"></sup>copies of the things in the heavens to be cleansed with these, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30129BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30129BN\"></sup>the heavenly things themselves with better sacrifices than these.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>For Christ <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30130BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30130BO\"></sup>did not enter a holy place made with hands, a <i>mere</i> copy of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30130BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30130BP\"></sup>the true one, but into <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30130BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30130BQ\"></sup>heaven itself, now <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30130BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30130BR\"></sup>to appear in the presence of God for us;",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>nor was it that He would offer Himself often, as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30131BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30131BS\"></sup>the high priest enters <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30131BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30131BT\"></sup>the holy place <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30131BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30131BU\"></sup>year by year with blood that is not his own.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>Otherwise, He would have needed to suffer often since <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30132BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30132BV\"></sup>the foundation of the world; but now <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30132BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30132BW\"></sup>once at <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30132BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30132BX\"></sup>the consummation of the ages He has been <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30132BY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BY&quot;&gt;BY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30132BY\"></sup>manifested to put away sin <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30132BZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BZ&quot;&gt;BZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30132BZ\"></sup>by the sacrifice of Himself.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>And inasmuch as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30133CA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CA&quot;&gt;CA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30133CA\"></sup>it is appointed for men to die once and after this <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30133CB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CB&quot;&gt;CB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30133CB\"></sup><i>comes</i> judgment,",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>so Christ also, having been <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30134CC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CC&quot;&gt;CC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30134CC\"></sup>offered once to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30134CD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CD&quot;&gt;CD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30134CD\"></sup>bear the sins of many, will appear <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30134CE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CE&quot;&gt;CE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30134CE\"></sup>a second time for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30134CF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CF&quot;&gt;CF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30134CF\"></sup>salvation <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30134CG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CG&quot;&gt;CG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30134CG\"></sup>without <i>reference to</i> sin, to those who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30134CH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CH&quot;&gt;CH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30134CH\"></sup>eagerly await Him."
		},
		"10": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">10 </span>For the Law, since it has <i>only</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30135A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30135A\"></sup>a shadow of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30135B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30135B\"></sup>the good things to come <i>and</i> not the very form of things, can <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30135C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30135C\"></sup>never, by the same sacrifices which they offer continually year by year, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30135D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30135D\"></sup>make perfect those who draw near.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Otherwise, would they not have ceased to be offered, because the worshipers, having once been cleansed, would no longer have had <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30136E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30136E\"></sup>consciousness of sins?",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30137F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30137F\"></sup>in those <i>sacrifices</i> there is a reminder of sins year by year.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>For it is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30138G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30138G\"></sup>impossible for the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30138H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30138H\"></sup>blood of bulls and goats to take away sins.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Therefore, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30139I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30139I\"></sup>when He comes into the world, He says,“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30139J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30139J\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Sacrifice and offering You have not desired</span>,<span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">But</span> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30139K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30139K\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">a body You have prepared for Me</span>;",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30140L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30140L\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">In whole burnt offerings and</span> <i>sacrifices</i> <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">for sin You have taken no pleasure</span>.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30141M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30141M\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Then I said, ‘Behold</span>, I <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">have come</span>(<span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">In</span> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30141N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30141N\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">the scroll of the book it is written of Me</span>)<span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">To do Your will</span>, O <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>.’”",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>After saying above, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30142O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30142O\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Sacrifices and offerings and</span> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30142P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30142P\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">whole burnt offerings and</span> <i>sacrifices</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30142Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30142Q\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">for sin You have not desired, nor have You taken pleasure</span> <i>in them</i>” (which are offered according to the Law),",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>then He said, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30143R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30143R\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Behold</span>, I <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">have come to do Your will</span>.” He takes away the first in order to establish the second.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>By this will we have been <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30144S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30144S\"></sup>sanctified through <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30144T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30144T\"></sup>the offering of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30144U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30144U\"></sup>the body of Jesus Christ <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30144V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30144V\"></sup>once for all.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Every priest stands daily ministering and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30145W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30145W\"></sup>offering time after time the same sacrifices, which <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30145X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30145X\"></sup>can never take away sins;",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>but He, having offered one sacrifice <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30146Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30146Y\"></sup>for sins <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30146Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30146Z\"></sup>for all time, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30146AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30146AA\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">sat down at the right hand of God</span>,",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>waiting from that time onward <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30147AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30147AB\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">until His enemies be made a footstool for His feet</span>.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>For by one offering He has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30148AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30148AC\"></sup>perfected <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30148AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30148AD\"></sup>for all time those who are sanctified.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30149AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30149AE\"></sup>the Holy Spirit also testifies to us; for after saying,",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30150AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30150AF\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">This is the covenant that I will make with them</span><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">After those days, says the Lord</span>:I <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">will put My laws upon their heart</span>,<span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">And on their mind I will write them</span>,”<i>He then says</i>,",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30151AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30151AG\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">And their sins and their lawless deeds</span>I <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">will remember no more</span>.”",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Now where there is forgiveness of these things, there is no longer <i>any</i> offering for sin.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Therefore, brethren, since we <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30153AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30153AH\"></sup>have confidence to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30153AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30153AI\"></sup>enter the holy place by the blood of Jesus,",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30154AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30154AJ\"></sup>a new and living way which He inaugurated for us through <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30154AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30154AK\"></sup>the veil, that is, His flesh,",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>and since <i>we have</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30155AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30155AL\"></sup>a great priest <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30155AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30155AM\"></sup>over the house of God,",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>let us <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30156AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30156AN\"></sup>draw near with a sincere heart in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30156AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30156AO\"></sup>full assurance of faith, having our hearts <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30156AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30156AP\"></sup>sprinkled <i>clean</i> from an evil conscience and our bodies <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30156AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30156AQ\"></sup>washed with pure water.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Let us hold fast the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30157AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30157AR\"></sup>confession of our <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30157AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30157AS\"></sup>hope without wavering, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30157AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30157AT\"></sup>He who promised is faithful;",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>and let us consider how <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30158AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30158AU\"></sup>to stimulate one another to love and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30158AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30158AV\"></sup>good deeds,",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>not forsaking our own <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30159AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30159AW\"></sup>assembling together, as is the habit of some, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30159AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30159AX\"></sup>encouraging <i>one another</i>; and all the more as you see <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30159AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30159AY\"></sup>the day drawing near.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>For if we go on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30160AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30160AZ\"></sup>sinning willfully after receiving <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30160BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30160BA\"></sup>the knowledge of the truth, there no longer remains a sacrifice for sins,",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>but a terrifying expectation of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30161BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30161BB\"></sup>judgment and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30161BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30161BC\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">the fury of a fire which will consume the adversaries</span>.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30162BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30162BD\"></sup>Anyone who has set aside the Law of Moses dies without mercy on <i>the testimony of</i> two or three witnesses.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30163BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30163BE\"></sup>How much severer punishment do you think he will deserve <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30163BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30163BF\"></sup>who has trampled under foot the Son of God, and has regarded as unclean <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30163BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30163BG\"></sup>the blood of the covenant <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30163BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30163BH\"></sup>by which he was sanctified, and has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30163BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30163BI\"></sup>insulted the Spirit of grace?",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>For we know Him who said, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30164BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30164BJ\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Vengeance is Mine</span>, I <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">will repay</span>.” And again, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30164BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30164BK\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">The Lord will judge His people</span>.”",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>It is a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30165BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30165BL\"></sup>terrifying thing to fall into the hands of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30165BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30165BM\"></sup>living God.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>But remember <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30166BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30166BN\"></sup>the former days, when, after being <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30166BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30166BO\"></sup>enlightened, you endured a great <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30166BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30166BP\"></sup>conflict of sufferings,",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>partly by being <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30167BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30167BQ\"></sup>made a public spectacle through reproaches and tribulations, and partly by becoming <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30167BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30167BR\"></sup>sharers with those who were so treated.",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>For you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30168BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30168BS\"></sup>showed sympathy to the prisoners and accepted <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30168BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30168BT\"></sup>joyfully the seizure of your property, knowing that you have for yourselves <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30168BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30168BU\"></sup>a better possession and a lasting one.",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>Therefore, do not throw away your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30169BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30169BV\"></sup>confidence, which has a great <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30169BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30169BW\"></sup>reward.",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>For you have need of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30170BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30170BX\"></sup>endurance, so that when you have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30170BY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BY&quot;&gt;BY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30170BY\"></sup>done the will of God, you may <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30170BZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BZ&quot;&gt;BZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30170BZ\"></sup>receive what was promised.",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30171CA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CA&quot;&gt;CA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30171CA\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">For yet in a very little while</span>,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30171CB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CB&quot;&gt;CB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30171CB\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">He who is coming will come, and will not delay</span>.",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30172CC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CC&quot;&gt;CC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30172CC\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">But My righteous one shall live by faith</span>;<span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">And if he shrinks back, My soul has no pleasure in him</span>.",
			"39": "<sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>But we are not of those who shrink back to destruction, but of those who have faith to the preserving of the soul."
		},
		"11": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">11 </span>Now faith is the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30174A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30174A\"></sup>assurance of <i>things</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30174B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30174B\"></sup>hoped for, the conviction of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30174C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30174C\"></sup>things not seen.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>For by it the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30175D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30175D\"></sup>men of old <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30175E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30175E\"></sup>gained approval.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>By faith we understand that the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30176F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30176F\"></sup>worlds were prepared <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30176G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30176G\"></sup>by the word of God, so that what is seen <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30176H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30176H\"></sup>was not made out of things which are visible.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>By faith <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30177I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30177I\"></sup>Abel offered to God a better sacrifice than Cain, through which he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30177J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30177J\"></sup>obtained the testimony that he was righteous, God testifying about his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30177K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30177K\"></sup>gifts, and through faith, though <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30177L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30177L\"></sup>he is dead, he still speaks.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>By faith <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30178M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30178M\"></sup>Enoch was taken up so that he would not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30178N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30178N\"></sup>see death; <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">and he was not found because God took him up</span>; for he obtained the witness that before his being taken up he was pleasing to God.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>And without faith it is impossible to please <i>Him</i>, for he who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30179O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30179O\"></sup>comes to God must believe that He is and <i>that</i> He is a rewarder of those who seek Him.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>By faith <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30180P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30180P\"></sup>Noah, being <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30180Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30180Q\"></sup>warned <i>by God</i> about <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30180R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30180R\"></sup>things not yet seen, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30180S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30180S\"></sup>in reverence <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30180T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30180T\"></sup>prepared an ark for the salvation of his household, by which he condemned the world, and became an heir of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30180U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30180U\"></sup>the righteousness which is according to faith.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>By faith <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30181V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30181V\"></sup>Abraham, when he was called, obeyed by going out to a place which he was to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30181W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30181W\"></sup>receive for an inheritance; and he went out, not knowing where he was going.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>By faith he lived as an alien in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30182X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30182X\"></sup>the land of promise, as in a foreign <i>land</i>, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30182Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30182Y\"></sup>dwelling in tents with Isaac and Jacob, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30182Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30182Z\"></sup>fellow heirs of the same promise;",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>for he was looking for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30183AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30183AA\"></sup>the city which has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30183AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30183AB\"></sup>foundations, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30183AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30183AC\"></sup>whose architect and builder is God.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>By faith even <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30184AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30184AD\"></sup>Sarah herself received ability to conceive, even beyond the proper time of life, since she considered Him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30184AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30184AE\"></sup>faithful who had promised.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Therefore there was born even of one man, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30185AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30185AF\"></sup>him as good as dead at that, <i>as many descendants</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30185AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30185AG\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">as the stars of heaven in number, and innumerable as the sand which is by the seashore</span>.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30186AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30186AH\"></sup>All these died in faith, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30186AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30186AI\"></sup>without receiving the promises, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30186AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30186AJ\"></sup>having seen them and having welcomed them from a distance, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30186AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30186AK\"></sup>having confessed that they were strangers and exiles on the earth.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>For those who say such things make it clear that they are seeking a country of their own.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>And indeed if they had been thinking of that <i>country</i> from which they went out, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30188AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30188AL\"></sup>they would have had opportunity to return.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>But as it is, they desire a better <i>country</i>, that is, a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30189AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30189AM\"></sup>heavenly one. Therefore <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30189AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30189AN\"></sup>God is not ashamed to be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30189AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30189AO\"></sup>called their God; for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30189AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30189AP\"></sup>He has prepared a city for them.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>By faith <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30190AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30190AQ\"></sup>Abraham, when he was tested, offered up Isaac, and he who had <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30190AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30190AR\"></sup>received the promises was offering up his only begotten <i>son</i>;",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><i>it was he</i> to whom it was said, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30191AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30191AS\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">In Isaac your</span> <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">descendants shall be called</span>.”",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>He considered that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30192AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30192AT\"></sup>God is able to raise <i>people</i> even from the dead, from which he also received him back as a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30192AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30192AU\"></sup>type.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>By faith <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30193AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30193AV\"></sup>Isaac blessed Jacob and Esau, even regarding things to come.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>By faith <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30194AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30194AW\"></sup>Jacob, as he was dying, blessed each of the sons of Joseph, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30194AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30194AX\"></sup>worshiped, <i>leaning</i> on the top of his staff.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>By faith <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30195AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30195AY\"></sup>Joseph, when he was dying, made mention of the exodus of the sons of Israel, and gave orders concerning his bones.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>By faith <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30196AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30196AZ\"></sup>Moses, when he was born, was hidden for three months by his parents, because they saw he was a beautiful child; and they were not afraid of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30196BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30196BA\"></sup>king’s edict.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>By faith Moses, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30197BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30197BB\"></sup>when he had grown up, refused to be called the son of Pharaoh’s daughter,",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>choosing rather to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30198BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30198BC\"></sup>endure ill-treatment with the people of God than to enjoy the passing pleasures of sin,",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30199BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30199BD\"></sup>considering the reproach of Christ greater riches than the treasures of Egypt; for he was looking to the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30199BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30199BE\"></sup>reward.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>By faith he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30200BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30200BF\"></sup>left Egypt, not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30200BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30200BG\"></sup>fearing the wrath of the king; for he endured, as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30200BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30200BH\"></sup>seeing Him who is unseen.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>By faith he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30201BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30201BI\"></sup>kept the Passover and the sprinkling of the blood, so that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30201BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30201BJ\"></sup>he who destroyed the firstborn would not touch them.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>By faith they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30202BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30202BK\"></sup>passed through the Red Sea as though <i>they were passing</i> through dry land; and the Egyptians, when they attempted it, were drowned.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>By faith <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30203BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30203BL\"></sup>the walls of Jericho fell down <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30203BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30203BM\"></sup>after they had been encircled for seven days.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>By faith <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30204BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30204BN\"></sup>Rahab the harlot did not perish along with those who were disobedient, after she had welcomed the spies in peace.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>And what more shall I say? For time will fail me if I tell of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30205BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30205BO\"></sup>Gideon, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30205BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30205BP\"></sup>Barak, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30205BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30205BQ\"></sup>Samson, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30205BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30205BR\"></sup>Jephthah, of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30205BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30205BS\"></sup>David and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30205BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30205BT\"></sup>Samuel and the prophets,",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>who by faith <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30206BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30206BU\"></sup>conquered kingdoms, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30206BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30206BV\"></sup>performed <i>acts of</i> righteousness, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30206BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30206BW\"></sup>obtained promises, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30206BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30206BX\"></sup>shut the mouths of lions,",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30207BY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BY&quot;&gt;BY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30207BY\"></sup>quenched the power of fire, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30207BZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BZ&quot;&gt;BZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30207BZ\"></sup>escaped the edge of the sword, from weakness were made strong, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30207CA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CA&quot;&gt;CA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30207CA\"></sup>became mighty in war, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30207CB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CB&quot;&gt;CB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30207CB\"></sup>put foreign armies to flight.",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30208CC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CC&quot;&gt;CC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30208CC\"></sup>Women received <i>back</i> their dead by resurrection; and others were tortured, not accepting their release, so that they might obtain a better resurrection;",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>and others experienced mockings and scourgings, yes, also <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30209CD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CD&quot;&gt;CD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30209CD\"></sup>chains and imprisonment.",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>They were <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30210CE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CE&quot;&gt;CE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30210CE\"></sup>stoned, they were <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30210CF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CF&quot;&gt;CF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30210CF\"></sup>sawn in two, they were tempted, they were <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30210CG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CG&quot;&gt;CG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30210CG\"></sup>put to death with the sword; they went about <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30210CH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CH&quot;&gt;CH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30210CH\"></sup>in sheepskins, in goatskins, being destitute, afflicted, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30210CI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CI&quot;&gt;CI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30210CI\"></sup>ill-treated",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>(<i>men</i> of whom the world was not worthy), <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30211CJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CJ&quot;&gt;CJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30211CJ\"></sup>wandering in deserts and mountains and caves and holes in the ground.",
			"39": "<sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>And all these, having <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30212CK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CK&quot;&gt;CK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30212CK\"></sup>gained approval through their faith, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30212CL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CL&quot;&gt;CL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30212CL\"></sup>did not receive what was promised,",
			"40": "<sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup>because God had provided <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30213CM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CM&quot;&gt;CM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30213CM\"></sup>something better for us, so that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30213CN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CN&quot;&gt;CN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30213CN\"></sup>apart from us they would not be made perfect."
		},
		"12": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">12 </span>Therefore, since we have so great a cloud of witnesses surrounding us, let us also <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30214A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30214A\"></sup>lay aside every encumbrance and the sin which so easily entangles us, and let us <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30214B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30214B\"></sup>run with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30214C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30214C\"></sup>endurance the race that is set before us,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>fixing our eyes on Jesus, the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30215D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30215D\"></sup>author and perfecter of faith, who for the joy set before Him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30215E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30215E\"></sup>endured the cross, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30215F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30215F\"></sup>despising the shame, and has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30215G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30215G\"></sup>sat down at the right hand of the throne of God.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30216H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30216H\"></sup>consider Him who has endured such hostility by sinners against Himself, so that you will not grow weary <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30216I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30216I\"></sup>and lose heart.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30217J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30217J\"></sup>You have not yet resisted <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30217K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30217K\"></sup>to the point of shedding blood in your striving against sin;",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>and you have forgotten the exhortation which is addressed to you as sons,“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30218L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30218L\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">My son, do not regard lightly the discipline of the Lord</span>,<span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Nor</span> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30218M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30218M\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">faint when you are reproved by Him</span>;",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30219N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30219N\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">For those</span> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30219O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30219O\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">whom the Lord loves He disciplines</span>,<span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">And He scourges every son whom He receives</span>.”",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>It is for discipline that you endure; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30220P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30220P\"></sup>God deals with you as with sons; for what son is there whom <i>his</i> father does not discipline?",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>But if you are without discipline, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30221Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30221Q\"></sup>of which all have become partakers, then you are illegitimate children and not sons.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Furthermore, we had earthly fathers to discipline us, and we <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30222R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30222R\"></sup>respected them; shall we not much rather be subject to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30222S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30222S\"></sup>the Father of spirits, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30222T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30222T\"></sup>live?",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>For they disciplined us for a short time as seemed best to them, but He <i>disciplines us</i> for <i>our</i> good, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30223U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30223U\"></sup>so that we may share His holiness.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>All discipline <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30224V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30224V\"></sup>for the moment seems not to be joyful, but sorrowful; yet to those who have been trained by it, afterwards it yields the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30224W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30224W\"></sup>peaceful fruit of righteousness.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Therefore, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30225X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30225X\"></sup>strengthen the hands that are weak and the knees that are feeble,",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30226Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30226Y\"></sup>make straight paths for your feet, so that <i>the limb</i> which is lame may not be put out of joint, but rather <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30226Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30226Z\"></sup>be healed.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30227AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30227AA\"></sup>Pursue peace with all men, and the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30227AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30227AB\"></sup>sanctification without which no one will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30227AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30227AC\"></sup>see the Lord.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>See to it that no one <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30228AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30228AD\"></sup>comes short of the grace of God; that no <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30228AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30228AE\"></sup>root of bitterness springing up causes trouble, and by it many be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30228AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30228AF\"></sup>defiled;",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>that <i>there be</i> no <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30229AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30229AG\"></sup>immoral or <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30229AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30229AH\"></sup>godless person like Esau, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30229AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30229AI\"></sup>who sold his own birthright for a <i>single</i> meal.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>For you know that even afterwards, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30230AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30230AJ\"></sup>when he desired to inherit the blessing, he was rejected, for he found no place for repentance, though he sought for it with tears.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30231AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30231AK\"></sup>For you have not come to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30231AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30231AL\"></sup><i>a mountain</i> that can be touched and to a blazing fire, and to darkness and gloom and whirlwind,",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>and to the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30232AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30232AM\"></sup>blast of a trumpet and the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30232AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30232AN\"></sup>sound of words which <i>sound was such that</i> those who heard <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30232AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30232AO\"></sup>begged that no further word be spoken to them.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>For they could not bear the command, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30233AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30233AP\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">If even a beast touches the mountain, it will be stoned</span>.”",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>And so terrible was the sight, <i>that</i> Moses said, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30234AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30234AQ\"></sup>I <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">am full of fear</span> and trembling.”",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30235AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30235AR\"></sup>you have come to Mount Zion and to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30235AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30235AS\"></sup>the city of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30235AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30235AT\"></sup>the living God, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30235AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30235AU\"></sup>the heavenly Jerusalem, and to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30235AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30235AV\"></sup>myriads of angels,",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>to the general assembly and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30236AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30236AW\"></sup>church of the firstborn who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30236AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30236AX\"></sup>are enrolled in heaven, and to God, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30236AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30236AY\"></sup>the Judge of all, and to the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30236AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30236AZ\"></sup>spirits of <i>the</i> righteous made perfect,",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>and to Jesus, the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30237BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30237BA\"></sup>mediator of a new covenant, and to the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30237BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30237BB\"></sup>sprinkled blood, which speaks better than <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30237BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30237BC\"></sup><i>the blood</i> of Abel.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30238BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30238BD\"></sup>See to it that you do not refuse Him who is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30238BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30238BE\"></sup>speaking. For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30238BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30238BF\"></sup>if those did not escape when they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30238BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30238BG\"></sup>refused him who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30238BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30238BH\"></sup>warned <i>them</i> on earth, much less <i>will</i> we <i>escape</i> who turn away from Him who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30238BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30238BI\"></sup><i>warns</i> from heaven.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30239BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30239BJ\"></sup>His voice shook the earth then, but now He has promised, saying, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30239BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30239BK\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Yet once more I will shake not only the earth, but also the heaven</span>.”",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>This <i>expression</i>, “Yet once more,” denotes <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30240BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30240BL\"></sup>the removing of those things which can be shaken, as of created things, so that those things which cannot be shaken may remain.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>Therefore, since we receive a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30241BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30241BM\"></sup>kingdom which cannot be shaken, let us show gratitude, by which we may <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30241BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30241BN\"></sup>offer to God an acceptable service with reverence and awe;",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30242BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30242BO\"></sup>our God is a consuming fire."
		},
		"13": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">13 </span>Let <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30243A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30243A\"></sup>love of the brethren continue.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Do not neglect to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30244B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30244B\"></sup>show hospitality to strangers, for by this some have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30244C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30244C\"></sup>entertained angels without knowing it.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30245D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30245D\"></sup>Remember <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30245E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30245E\"></sup>the prisoners, as though in prison with them, <i>and</i> those who are ill-treated, since you yourselves also are in the body.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30246F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30246F\"></sup>Marriage <i>is to be held</i> in honor among all, and the <i>marriage</i> bed <i>is to be</i> undefiled; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30246G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30246G\"></sup>for fornicators and adulterers God will judge.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><i>Make sure that</i> your character is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30247H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30247H\"></sup>free from the love of money, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30247I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30247I\"></sup>being content with what you have; for He Himself has said, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30247J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30247J\"></sup>I <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">will never desert you, nor will I ever forsake you</span>,”",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>so that we confidently say,“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30248K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30248K\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">The Lord is my helper</span>, I <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">will not be afraid</span>.<span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">What will man do to me</span>?”",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Remember <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30249L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30249L\"></sup>those who led you, who spoke <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30249M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30249M\"></sup>the word of God to you; and considering the result of their conduct, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30249N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30249N\"></sup>imitate their faith.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30250O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30250O\"></sup>Jesus Christ <i>is</i> the same yesterday and today and forever.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30251P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30251P\"></sup>Do not be carried away by varied and strange teachings; for it is good for the heart to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30251Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30251Q\"></sup>be strengthened by grace, not by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30251R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30251R\"></sup>foods, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30251S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30251S\"></sup>through which those who were so occupied were not benefited.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>We have an altar <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30252T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30252T\"></sup>from which those <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30252U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30252U\"></sup>who serve the tabernacle have no right to eat.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30253V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30253V\"></sup>the bodies of those animals whose blood is brought into the holy place by the high priest <i>as an offering</i> for sin, are burned outside the camp.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Therefore Jesus also, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30254W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30254W\"></sup>that He might sanctify the people <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30254X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30254X\"></sup>through His own blood, suffered <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30254Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30254Y\"></sup>outside the gate.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>So, let us go out to Him outside the camp, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30255Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30255Z\"></sup>bearing His reproach.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>For here <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30256AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30256AA\"></sup>we do not have a lasting city, but we are seeking <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30256AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30256AB\"></sup><i>the city</i> which is to come.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30257AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30257AC\"></sup>Through Him then, let us continually offer up a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30257AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30257AD\"></sup>sacrifice of praise to God, that is, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30257AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30257AE\"></sup>the fruit of lips that give thanks to His name.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>And do not neglect doing good and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30258AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30258AF\"></sup>sharing, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30258AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30258AG\"></sup>with such sacrifices God is pleased.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30259AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30259AH\"></sup>Obey your leaders and submit <i>to them</i>, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30259AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30259AI\"></sup>they keep watch over your souls as those who will give an account. Let them do this with joy and not with grief, for this would be unprofitable for you.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30260AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30260AJ\"></sup>Pray for us, for we are sure that we have a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30260AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30260AK\"></sup>good conscience, desiring to conduct ourselves honorably in all things.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>And I urge <i>you</i> all the more to do this, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30261AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30261AL\"></sup>so that I may be restored to you the sooner.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Now <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30262AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30262AM\"></sup>the God of peace, who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30262AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30262AN\"></sup>brought up from the dead the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30262AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30262AO\"></sup>great Shepherd of the sheep through <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30262AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30262AP\"></sup>the blood of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30262AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30262AQ\"></sup>eternal covenant, <i>even</i> Jesus our Lord,",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30263AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30263AR\"></sup>equip you in every good thing to do His will, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30263AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30263AS\"></sup>working in us that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30263AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30263AT\"></sup>which is pleasing in His sight, through Jesus Christ, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30263AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30263AU\"></sup>to whom <i>be</i> the glory forever and ever. Amen.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30264AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30264AV\"></sup>I urge you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30264AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30264AW\"></sup>brethren, bear with this <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30264AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30264AX\"></sup>word of exhortation, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30264AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30264AY\"></sup>I have written to you briefly.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Take notice that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30265AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30265AZ\"></sup>our brother Timothy has been released, with whom, if he comes soon, I will see you.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Greet <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30266BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30266BA\"></sup>all of your leaders and all the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30266BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30266BB\"></sup>saints. Those from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30266BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30266BC\"></sup>Italy greet you.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30267BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30267BD\"></sup>Grace be with you all."
		}
	}
};
module.exports = book;